{"tid":1362243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話係住鄉村要評論鄉村內政治，可唔可以post住址證明核實身份？","createTime":"2019-07-24T22:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T23:24:16.000Z","uid":175882,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"11302f29c49637b96265668240c85062b5214af2","tid":1362243,"uid":175882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T22:25:34.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，非村民有野想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由於727港人當日行動仍有很多未知之數，好多熱心示威人士仲怕入到元朗會唔會被襲擊，又唔知對抗邊條村，邊條村中立<br />\n所以我覺得凡係表明自己係住村並且開post評論各村恩怨/立場/習俗嘅，應該post住址證明（例如煤氣單、水費單），以防三毛俾假消息分化<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不分化，不割蓆，we connect，be water"},{"pid":"68245002c41a8a0cef57a2fbe7a86beb20fd2913","tid":1362243,"uid":61398,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T22:27:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a41a628a6ee875eabbb34c29b259377dae3fdb3","tid":1362243,"uid":58841,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T22:28:27.000Z","msg":"POST住址證明你係咪傻撚左"},{"pid":"df79e87c39f6a3768516fb2f5cc71f1f63c28d91","tid":1362243,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T22:30:04.000Z","msg":"怕被三毛分化就唔該用下自己個腦學識獨立思考<br />\n而唔係叫人POST住址證明等佢地俾黑社會搞"},{"pid":"3413e4664f74a7c0fe425820bd6c6bd2430c1b0f","tid":1362243,"uid":175882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a41a628a6ee875eabbb34c29b259377dae3fdb3","tid":1362243,"uid":58841,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T22:28:27.000Z","msg":"POST住址證明你係咪傻撚左"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T22:31:06.000Z","msg":"留返水電煤/銀行/可信賴公司logo+地址包括村名就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89264abb879dd3558ca785899278e3b245cf463d","tid":1362243,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3413e4664f74a7c0fe425820bd6c6bd2430c1b0f","tid":1362243,"uid":175882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a41a628a6ee875eabbb34c29